symbol: The gene symbol associated with the variant.
allele: The variant allele observed in the sample.
impact: The predicted impact of the variant on the gene or protein function.
gnomadg_af: The allele frequency of the variant in the gnomAD genome dataset.
max_af: The maximum allele frequency observed in any population dataset.
revel: The REVEL score predicting the pathogenicity of missense variants.
sift: The SIFT score predicting the effect of amino acid substitutions on protein function.
